task.summary:
Create booklist page. Create classes: 1. Entity layer: Book 2. DAO Layer: BookDao interface and its implementation BookDaoImpl
Also include libs in pom.xml
Connect to H2 Database. Create application-context.xml and connect H2DB to app. Rewrite BookDaoImpl methods, now data push/pop to/from database.
Add user controller and user form
Add BookDaoTest and UserDaoTest classes (unfortunately don't work)
Add BookController and make a bit refactoring
Add CartDao and it's implementation. Now you can make orders!
Add Service layer, delete home controller and make some refactoring.
Add isBookAlreadyInCart method. Now application catches when when we have two or more same books and merges them to one increasing the bookCount value. Refactor code a bit.
